# Hello Demo Action

A simple dummy GitHub Action that greets a user by name.

## Usage
```yaml
- uses: your-username/hello-greet-action@v1
  with:
    who-to-greet: "Aarav"
```

## Inputs
| Input | Description | Required | Default |
|-------|-------------|----------|---------|
| `who-to-greet` | Name of the person to greet | Yes | `World` |

## Outputs
| Output | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| `greeting-time` | Time the greeting was delivered |
